---

<section class="code-compare section reveal" id="compare">
  <div class="compare-container container">
    <div class="compare-header reveal delay-100">
      <h2 class="section-title">The <span class="accent-text">end of</span> manual case review.</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Stop spending 30 minutes per ICSR report. Gemmra processes each case in ~8.5 seconds with full audit trail.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="compare-split reveal delay-200">
      
      <!-- The Old Way -->
      <div class="code-panel old-way">
        <div class="panel-header">
          <span class="panel-label error-label">Manual Review</span>
          <span class="file-name">ICSR Workflow</span>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body">
          <pre><code><span class="keyword">📋 Manual ICSR Review Process:</span>

1. Read case narrative (~5 min)
2. Check ICH E2A seriousness criteria (~5 min)
3. Search MedDRA dictionary (~8 min)
4. Cross-reference drug label (~7 min)
5. Assess WHO-UMC causality (~5 min)
6. Write structured report (~10 min)

⏱ Total: ~30 minutes per case
📊 2,000,000 cases/year (FDA alone)
💰 $20 per case = $40M+/year</code></pre>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-footer error-footer">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line></svg>
          ✗ Slow, inconsistent, unscalable.
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- The Gemmra Way -->
      <div class="code-panel new-way">
        <div class="panel-header">
          <span class="panel-label success-label">The Gemmra Way</span>
          <span class="file-name">AI Pipeline</span>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body">
          <pre><code><span class="keyword">🧠 Gemmra AI Assessment:</span>

Input: Case narrative
  ↓
<span class="comment">&lt;thinking&gt;
  Analyzing ICH E2A criteria...
  Mapping to MedDRA ontology...
  Checking drug label database...
  Evaluating WHO-UMC causality...
&lt;/thinking&gt;</span>
  ↓
Output: 4 structured assessments
  with auditable reasoning trace

⏱ Total: ~8.5 seconds per case
💰 $0.01 per case = $20K/year</code></pre>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-footer success-footer">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
          ✓ Fast. Auditable. 2,000× cheaper.
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .compare-container {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .compare-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .compare-split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .code-panel {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-card);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    transition: transform var(--transition-base), box-shadow var(--transition-base);
    position: relative;
  }

  .new-way {
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
    border-color: var(--border-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), 0 0 20px var(--accent-glow);
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }

  /* Deep Space Edge Highlight */
  .new-way::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: inherit;
    padding: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.5) 0%, transparent 50%);
    -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
    -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
    mask-composite: exclude;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .panel-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
  }

  .panel-label {
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .error-label { background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1); color: var(--color-error); }
  .success-label { background: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.15); color: var(--accent-primary); box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent-glow); }

  .file-name {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .panel-body {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    flex-grow: 1;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  pre {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: clamp(12px, 1.5cqw, 14px); /* Fluid type based on container */
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .comment { color: var(--text-muted); font-style: italic; }
  .keyword { color: var(--accent-secondary); font-weight: 600; }

  .panel-footer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .error-footer { color: var(--color-error); }
  .success-footer { color: var(--accent-primary); text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent-glow); }

  /* Fluid Architecture via Standard Media Queries */
  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .compare-split {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-3xl);
    }
    .new-way {
      transform: none; /* remove scale on mobile */
    }
  }
</style>
